originalText.text:
Dr Ethan is very knowledgeable in his field. I went to him for a back issue and he ensured that in each session, I was not only getting adjusted, but was also working on learning different movements that I could practice during the week.

He listens to the challenges carefully, is able to adapt his approach to meet me where I am at and most importantly, he clearly walks me through the reason for his selected line of treatment.

I also appreciated that he genuinely cared about seeing improvements week by week.

I definitely recommend him for any musculature related issue !

originalText.text:
I hurt my knee while training for a marathon, and I always had back pain too. But then, I went to see Dr. Ethan for chiropractic care. He used different techniques like massaging, cupping, and even some physical therapy stuff. It really helped!

My back pain got better, and my knee started feeling way better too after just three sessions with him. I definitely think Dr. Ethan is great, and I would tell anyone to go see him if they need help like I did. He’s super good at what he does, and I’m really thankful for his help. Now, I’m back on track to reach my marathon goals!

Laura
